                "invention-title": [
                    "Device for catalytic cracking of ammonia gas",
                    "一种用于氨气催化裂解的装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a device for catalytic cracking of ammonia gas. The device comprises a cracking device and a control system thereof. Wherein the cracking device comprises a cracker and a pipeline system; the pipeline system comprises a primary air branch, a secondary air branch, an ammonia gas combustion branch and an ammonia gas cracking branch; air of the primary air branch and the secondary air branch and ammonia gas of the combustion ammonia gas branch are introduced into the plasma-assisted ammonia combustion heat exchange section for plasma-assisted ammonia combustion, and ammonia gas of the cracking ammonia gas branch is introduced into a cracking cavity of the cracker for catalytic ammonia cracking; the cracking device control system monitors the temperature in the cracking device and the hydrogen concentration of ammonia-hydrogen mixed gas in an outlet buffer tank, and the cracking device works in a set state by adjusting the flow of ammonia gas and air introduced into the plasma auxiliary ammonia combustion heat exchange section; the cracking device can stably output ammonia-hydrogen mixed gas with specific temperature, pressure and hydrogen concentration, and the ammonia-hydrogen mixed gas can be introduced into an engine system for application."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种用于氨气催化裂解的装置包括裂解装置及其控制系统。其中，裂解装置包括裂解器和管路系统；管路系统包括一次空气支路、二次空气支路、燃烧氨气支路和裂解氨气支路；一次空气支路和二次空气支路的空气以及燃烧氨气支路的氨气通入到等离子体辅助氨燃烧换热段内进行等离子体辅助氨燃烧，裂解氨气支路的氨气通入到裂解器的裂解腔体内部进行催化氨裂解；裂解装置控制系统对裂解装置中的温度以及出口缓存罐中氨氢混合气的氢气浓度进行监测，通过调节通入到等离子体辅助氨燃烧换热段内部的氨气和空气的流量，使裂解器工作在设定状态，实现裂解装置稳定输出特定温度、压力和氢气浓度的氨氢混合气，该氨氢混合气即可通入到发动机系统中进行应用。"
                }
            ]
